 photo from Amien . Saturday 23.6.17 Grant a day leav to Amien but fail to take advantag of it . Walk to Albert about 4 mile , spent a few hour there came back by Coal waggon to Millencourt walk from there to camp . Great improv in Albert ; becom more popul daili . Receiv mail 22 29 April from home on my return . Weild the willow for an hour or so at night . Four more went to Blighti on leav . Sunday 24.6.17 Wrote my usual week letter . Play cricket in even Monday 25.6.17 Mix up by Order offic on earli
